attributes.review:
DONALD TRUMP SUPPORTERS: do not get this app. It is Absolutely Devastating. I read other views, thinking they were just jokes, but they are real. The rumors are true. This app looks for all personal information on the iPhones and telephones and all of the cellular phones. I have no choice but to believe that the cause of this issue is Voldemort himself. That is why nobody has heard from him. Now, I will list the Issues I had with the app:
I could not find it after I downloaded it. Once I finally got my granddaughter to find it for me, we sat in completely uninterrupted silence for 41 minutes waiting for this app to load. Next, the only wait to log in is by giving this app PERSONAL INFORMATION. This includes my phone number and my email. What kind of request is that in a democracy?
Finally, my granddaughter decided we should delete the app which took us another 92 minutes, for which we sat, again, in bone-chilling silence caused completely by the downloading of the app. This is the first app I have ever downloaded ever, and it was a Terrible Experience.
